</SPAN></FONT><FONT COLOR="#990000"><FONT FACE="Times New Roman, serif"><FONT SIZE=5><SPAN LANG="en-US"><b>衡文宮/彰化縣</b></SPAN></FONT></FONT></FONT></SPAN></FONT><br>
<br>
<br>
